"n.独裁主义者；极权主义者 【英】 n.极权主义者(person who believes in complete obedience to authority) 【记】 来自authority(权威 ，权力)，author(作 家，有权的人) n. 独裁主义者(与个人自由相反, 赞成绝对服从权威) 【记】authority(n 权威, 权力) 【记】authority 权威 + ian人 authoritarian (adj.)  1862, ""favoring imposed order over freedom,"" from authority + -an. Compare authoritative, which originally had this meaning to itself. Noun in the sense of one advocating or practicing such governance is from 1859."
